Package dao

Class TweetDAOImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • dao.TweetDAOImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEntityDAO
    public class TweetDAOImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEntityDAO
    An implementation of the IEntityDAO interface. This class is used to handle data and get Tweet objects. In addition to implementing the IEntityDAO interface, this class provides a method to valid input data.

    This class is only responsible for generating Tweet objects according to the input data, and then store these Tweet objects into a queue. Since that Tweet objects are needed to be sorted, so PriorityQueue is used to do sort automatically. The compareTo()} method of Tweet entity is overrided so that the first element in PriorityQueue would be the biggest one, rather than the smallest by default. When the traverse of excel file is done, TweetDAO will return its queue.
